videos.headline: Nakia Cheatham buries the corner 3 for Alcorn State
videos.description: Nakia Cheatham pulls up and knocks down the triple from the corner to pad the Lady Braves' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Nakia Cheatham buries the corner 3 for Alcorn State) 2024/03/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anijah Grant's 2nd effort pays off for a Grambling State bucket
videos.description: Anijah Grant lays in the offensive board to pad the Tigers' lead in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Anijah Grant's 2nd effort pays off for a Grambling State bucket) 2024/03/15 ESHEET
